{{vgname|花|en=Flower}}是一款由[[ThatGameCompany|ThatGameCompany]]开发，發行于[[PlayStation_3|PlayStation 3]]平台[[PlayStation_Network|PlayStation Network]]上的數字版游戏。游戏初次公开於2007年[[东京电玩展|东京电玩展]]上，<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.joystiq.com/2007/11/29/flow-dev-discusses-blossoming-new-project/|title=FlOw dev discusses blossoming new project|publisher=Joystiq|author=Ross Miller|date=2007-11-29|accessdate=2008-08-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20081012173458/http://www.joystiq.com/2007/11/29/flow-dev-discusses-blossoming-new-project/|archive-date=2008-10-12|dead-url=yes}}</ref>并於2009年2月12日發行。<ref name=NARelease>{{cite web|url=http://blog.us.playstation.com/2009/01/19/stop-and-smell-the-flower-on-psn-february-12th/|title=Stop and smell the Flower on PSN February 12th|publisher=SCEA|accessdate=2009-07-02|archive-date=2009-06-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090618060023/http://blog.us.playstation.com/2009/01/19/stop-and-smell-the-flower-on-psn-february-12th/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name=EURelease>{{cite web|url=http://www.eurogamer.net/articles/sony-prices-flower-up|title=Flower to cost just over six quid in Europe|publisher=Eurogamer|date=2009-02-02|accessdate=2009-07-02|archive-date=2009-06-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090611040240/http://www.eurogamer.net/articles/sony-prices-flower-up|dead-url=no}}</ref>制作人[[陈星汉|陈星汉]]在开发过程中表示：“我们开始时并不知道在做什么，只是心中存有这么一个概念：每一台PlayStation都像是你客厅中的一个入口，可以带你通往别处。于是我就想，要是这是这一入口能带你重返自然，那该有多好。 ”<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.exclaim.ca/articles/multiarticlesub.aspx?csid1=130&csid2=807&fid1=36732 |title=存档副本 |accessdate=2015-12-22 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20090317235322/http://www.exclaim.ca/articles/multiarticlesub.aspx?csid1=130&csid2=807&fid1=36732 |archivedate=2009-03-17 }}</ref>

== 概述 ==
[[Image:Flower_screen01.jpg|thumb]]
游戏每关都发生在不同的花的梦中，起初它开在一座阴沉都市中的公寓窗台上。游戏的目的在于将这朵花的花瓣引至大地上的其他花朵处，并让各色花朵向游戏世界中的四方迅速蔓延。随着玩家游戏进程的深入，城市和公寓会变得愈渐鲜活多彩，直至达到100％完成状态，游戏背景中原有的街景也会被生机勃勃的山色取代。玩家可以通过控制动作感应手柄来引导[[花瓣|花瓣]]穿越过五光十色的大地，按下手柄的任意按钮均可加速。<ref name="It's awesome: Flower PS3">{{cite web|url=http://www.ps3fanboy.com/2008/07/16/its-awesome-flower-ps3/|title=It's awesome: Flower (PS3)|publisher=PS3 Fanboy (Joystiq)|accessdate=2009-07-02|archive-date=2009-01-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090123085535/http://www.ps3fanboy.com/2008/07/16/its-awesome-flower-ps3|dead-url=no}}</ref>

《花》采用PlayStation 3的[[DualShock_3|六轴]]运动控制手柄，用以操作花瓣周游地图。<ref name="It's awesome: Flower PS3"/>

== 開發 ==
2013年10月，索尼宣布包括本作在内的4款优秀独立游戏将在2013年11月登陆[[PlayStation_4|PlayStation 4]]和[[PlayStation_Vita|PlayStation Vita]]平台。<ref name="PSVPS4">{{cite web|url=http://blog.us.playstation.com/2013/10/16/flower-flow-sound-shapes-escape-plan-coming-to-ps4/|title=Flower, flOw, Sound Shapes, Escape Plan Coming to PS4|publisher=索尼电脑娱乐北美|author=Nathan Gary|date=2013-10-16|accessdate=2013-10-17|archive-date=2015-09-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150908022358/http://blog.us.playstation.com/2013/10/16/flower-flow-sound-shapes-escape-plan-coming-to-ps4/|dead-url=no}}</ref>

2019年2月，由[[Annapurna_Interactive|Annapurna Interactive]]在Steam、GoG以及EpicStore等数字游戏平台发售本作的[[Windows|Microsoft Windows]]版本。<ref>[https://www.gcores.com/articles/106428 携着花瓣的那阵风，终于吹到了你的电脑上：《Flower》正式登陆PC平台] {{Wayback|url=https://www.gcores.com/articles/106428 |date=20190226234205 }}.机核网.2019-02-15.[2019-02-26].</ref>
